# Without this, core.autocrlf (on by default on Windows) can misdetect
# keras_metadata.pb as text and corrupt it with LF->CRLF conversion on
# checkout — happened once, silently broke model loading. Everything under
# artifacts/ and data/ is either a trained-model binary or an image; none of
# it should ever go through line-ending translation.
artifacts/** binary
data/** binary
data_pending/** binary
samples/** binary
*.npz binary
*.pb binary
*.tif binary
*.tiff binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.png binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
*.ttf binary
*.eot binary
*.otf binary
